{"tid":735023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外賣員接恐怖Order　客人：上樓要戴護身符","createTime":"2018-07-09T06:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T13:05:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"69b6928dd79acd5e8de43f978eb03e10bc2e6112","tid":735023,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/photo/bkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180709134919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180709%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180709134919&h=72bacb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼節未到都咁猛？網上流傳一張外賣送餐紙，顯示有食客在備註一欄聲稱該樓層「有靈體」，提醒外賣員「必須佩戴護身符」！ <br />\n<br />\n據該張外賣紙顯示，送餐地點為九龍藍田平田邨平旺樓一個單位，點餐時間為上周六（7日）深夜時分。據備註一欄所寫，「此地址層樓有靈體，備註外賣員不必要看防煙門、後樓梯。最好必須唸經帶護身符前來，免得日後遭遇麻煩。」 <br />\n<br />\n點餐紙似是惡作劇，而翻查資料，平旺樓去年發生過命案。2017年9月21日，一名56歲男子疑因感情問題，留下遺書後在單位內燒炭自殺。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/photo/bkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180709134919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180709%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180709134919&h=ab81079f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上亦流傳另一張送餐紙，顯示有客人要求外賣員跟食客講「生日快樂」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/bkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180709%2Fbkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001.html&d=o3r6j3M7AqXltrNppPm1YaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=68a38801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180709/bkn-20180709112227389-0709_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"530cbece0972066ab516351bfc63df8065037675","tid":735023,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"